00:34:45.480 --> 00:34:46.790
dahil mayroon kang mga inaasahan

00:34:46.790 --> 00:34:47.910
ng Marquis ng Zhenguo,

00:34:48.070 --> 00:34:49.480
ibig sabihin meron ka na

00:34:49.710 --> 00:34:50.710
isang plano laban sa North Qi?

